  "texts": [
    "A Convolutional Neural Network (CNN) is a kind of artificial NN that is particularly effective at analyzing visual data.",
    "This approach integrates attributes with subtle visual cues to enhance the precision of reidentification.",
    "Vu and Huang [13] devised a multitask convolutional neural network (CNN) that simultaneously acquired knowledge on the center position, size, displacement, and semantic advancements.",
    "This CNN was purposefully designed for the sole objective of detecting pedestrians.",
    "A comprehensive semantic segmentation technique was created in [14], which replaced the single category \"person\" with nine different attribute categories.However, most existing researching algorithms are restricted by the capacity of human-defined ascribes to effectively represent the required features."
  ],
